---------------------------------------------------------------

Requirements:

 - Console Ngaro VM
   *** Not curses based ***
 - The included image file
 - colors.retro

To use:

 retro --with colors.retro

Read the help text.

Updates to code at http://github.com/crcx/colors

Windows is *not* supported at this time. Sorry.
